---
const skills = {
  Frontend: [
    { name: "HTML5", icon: "https://cdn.simpleicons.org/html5/E34F26" },
    { name: "CSS3", icon: "https://cdn.simpleicons.org/css3/1572B6" },
    {
      name: "JavaScript",
      icon: "https://cdn.simpleicons.org/javascript/F7DF1E",
    },
    {
      name: "TypeScript",
      icon: "https://cdn.simpleicons.org/typescript/3178C6",
    },
    { name: "React", icon: "https://cdn.simpleicons.org/react/61DAFB" },
    { name: "Astro", icon: "https://cdn.simpleicons.org/astro/FF5D01" },
    { name: "Next.js", icon: "https://cdn.simpleicons.org/nextdotjs/000000" },
    {
      name: "Tailwind CSS",
      icon: "https://cdn.simpleicons.org/tailwindcss/06B6D4",
    },
  ],
  Herramientas: [
    { name: "Git", icon: "https://cdn.simpleicons.org/git/F05032" },
    { name: "GitHub", icon: "https://cdn.simpleicons.org/github/181717" },
    { name: "Vite", icon: "https://cdn.simpleicons.org/vite/646CFF" },
    { name: "ESLint", icon: "https://cdn.simpleicons.org/eslint/4B32C3" },
    { name: "Prettier", icon: "https://cdn.simpleicons.org/prettier/F7B93E" },
  ],
  Testing: [
    { name: "Jest", icon: "https://cdn.simpleicons.org/jest/C21325" },
    {
      name: "React Testing Library",
      icon: "https://cdn.simpleicons.org/testinglibrary/E33332",
    },
  ],
  "Performance y Accesibilidad": [
    {
      name: "Lighthouse",
      icon: "https://cdn.simpleicons.org/lighthouse/FF6D00",
    },
    {
      name: "DevTools",
      icon: "https://cdn.simpleicons.org/googlechrome/4285F4",
    },
  ],
};
---

<section
  id="skills"
  class="py-24 px-6 md:px-12 max-w-screen-xl mx-auto text-center space-y-12"
>
  <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-dark dark:text-light">
    Tecnologías
  </h2>

  <div class="space-y-16">
    {
      Object.entries(skills).map(([group, techs]) => (
        <div class="space-y-6" data-reveal>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-dark dark:text-light">
            {group}
          </h3>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-2 sm:grid-cols-3 md:grid-cols-5 gap-8 place-items-center">
            {techs.map((skill) => (
              <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-2">
                <img src={skill.icon} alt={skill.name} class="w-12 h-12" />
                <span class="text-sm text-dark dark:text-light">
                  {skill.name}
                </span>
              </div>
            ))}
          </div>
        </div>
      ))
    }
  </div>

  <div
    class="text-sm text-dark/70 dark:text-light/60 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed"
    data-reveal
  >
    Desarrollo sitios web modernos utilizando tecnologías como Astro, Tailwind
    CSS y React, enfocándome en rendimiento, accesibilidad y buenas prácticas.
    Utilizo herramientas como Git y GitHub para mantener flujos de trabajo
    organizados y colaborativos.
  </div>
</section>
